title: BRIEF-Piteco H1 net profit rises by 38 pct yoy to 1.3 million euros
text:
BRIEF-Piteco H1 net profit rises by 38 pct yoy to 1.3 million euros Sept 29 
* H1 net profit 1.3 million euros ($1.46 million), up 38.0 percent year on year 
* H1 revenue 6.1 million euros, up 9.0 percent year on year 
Source text: bit.ly/1H5AgEK Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8921 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
